Eliaquim Mangala is British football's most expensive defender ever, but the new Manchester City recruit was put through his paces in training on Tuesday, and may have realised the step up from the Portuguese League to the Premier League is bigger than he thought.

Signed for £32million from Porto, Mangala was pictured in his first training session at Carrington marking Sergio Aguero and Co.

